                                                                                                                                                      [1B[38;5;231m**Parent design:** cb-7aa91d[39m                                                                                                                               [1B[38;5;231m**Wave:** 2[39m                                                                                                                                                [1B[38;5;231m**Depends on:** Task A (Stop hook must exist so the fix flow completes reliably)[39m                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Repo:** cobuild[39m                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Scope[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mCreate the new `fix` phase for bugs. This is the single-session replacement for the two-phase investigate+implement flow. The agent does lightweight [39m      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231minvestigation as part of fixing, in one tmux window, with the Stop hook handling completion.[39m                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Changes[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. Create `skills/fix/fix-bug.md` with YAML frontmatter (name, description, summary, version) and the following structure:[39m                                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - **What this is** — one-session bug fix[39m                                                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - **Escalation check** — read the escalation criteria, if any apply, STOP and add `needs-investigation` label instead of proceeding[39m                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - **Procedure**:[39m                                                                                                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     1. Read the bug report and any linked context[39m                                                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     2. Reproduce if possible[39m                                                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     3. Light investigation — check code, git blame, recent changes, related tests[39m                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     4. Append findings to the bug body: `cobuild wi append <bug-id> --body "## Findings\n..."`[39m                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     5. Implement the fix[39m                                                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     6. Run tests and build[39m                                                                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     7. Commit (Stop hook will run `cobuild complete`)[39m                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - **Self-escalation protocol** — when to stop mid-session and escalate[39m                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - **Gotchas section** (empty, populated over time)[39m                                                                                                      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Add `fix` phase to `examples/pipeline.yaml`:[39m                                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```yaml[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   phases:[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     fix:[39m                                                                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       skill: fix/fix-bug.md[39m                                                                                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   workflows:[39m                                                                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     bug:[39m                                                                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       phases: [fix, review, done][39m                                                                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     bug-complex:[39m                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       phases: [investigate, implement, review, done][39m                                                                                                      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```[39m                                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m3. Add `fix` to the default config in `internal/config/config.go` (DefaultConfig) so it works zero-config[39m                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
