                                                                                                                                                      [1B[38;5;231m**Parent design:** cb-7aa91d[39m                                                                                                                               [1B[38;5;231m**Wave:** 2[39m                                                                                                                                                [1B[38;5;231m**Depends on:** Task C (the `fix` phase must exist first)[39m                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Repo:** cobuild[39m                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Scope[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mUpdate `internal/cmd/dispatch.go` phase inference to route bugs to the new `fix` phase by default, with escalation to the read-only `investigate` phase [39m   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mwhen the bug is labeled `needs-investigation`.[39m                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Changes[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. `internal/cmd/dispatch.go` — replace the current bug phase inference:[39m                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```go[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   case "bug":[39m                                                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       if hasLabel(task, "needs-investigation") {[39m                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m           currentPhase = "investigate"[39m                                                                                                                    [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       } else {[39m                                                                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m           currentPhase = "fix"[39m                                                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       }[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```[39m                                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Add helper `hasLabel(task *connector.WorkItem, label string) bool` if it does not exist — check `task.Labels` slice[39m                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m3. Add phase prompt handling for `fix` in `writePhasePrompt`:[39m                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```go[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   case "fix":[39m                                                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       b.WriteString("**Fix this bug.**\n\n")[39m                                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       b.WriteString("Follow the fix-bug skill:\n")[39m                                                                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       b.WriteString("1. Read the bug report\n")[39m                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       b.WriteString("2. Check escalation criteria — if any apply, add `needs-investigation` label and stop\n")[39m                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       b.WriteString("3. Reproduce, investigate lightly, append findings to the bug\n")[39m                                                                    [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       b.WriteString("4. Implement the fix, run tests, build\n")[39m                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       b.WriteString("5. Commit — the Stop hook will run `cobuild complete`\n")[39m                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```[39m                                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Acceptance criteria[39m                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `hasLabel` helper exists and correctly detects labels on `WorkItem`[39m                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] Bug with no `needs-investigation` label dispatches to `fix` phase[39m                                                                                    [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] Bug with `needs-investigation` label dispatches to `investigate` phase (unchanged behavior for this case)[39m                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `writePhasePrompt` has a `fix` case producing the new prompt[39m                                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] Unit test or integration test verifies both routing paths[39m                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `go build ./...` and `go vet ./...` pass[39m                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
