                                                                                                                                                      [1B[38;5;231m**Parent design:** cb-7aa91d[39m                                                                                                                               [1B[38;5;231m**Wave:** 2[39m                                                                                                                                                [1B[38;5;231m**Depends on:** Task C, Task D[39m                                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Repo:** cobuild[39m                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Scope[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mBelt-and-braces for RC1. Even if a bug is routed to the investigate phase (via the `needs-investigation` label), if its body already contains [39m             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231minvestigation content from a prior conversation, do not inject contradictory read-only instructions. Instead, transparently downgrade to the `fix` phase [39m  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mand log a notice.[39m                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Changes[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. `internal/cmd/dispatch.go` — after phase inference, before writing the prompt:[39m                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```go[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   if currentPhase == "investigate" && hasInvestigationContent(task.Content) {[39m                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       fmt.Printf("Notice: bug %s already has investigation content — routing to fix phase instead\n", task.ID)[39m                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m       currentPhase = "fix"[39m                                                                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   }[39m                                                                                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   ```[39m                                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Add helper `hasInvestigationContent(content string) bool` in `internal/cmd/dispatch.go`:[39m                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - Returns true if the body contains any of: `## Investigation Report`, `## Root Cause`, `## Fix Applied`, `## Fix` (at heading level 2)[39m                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - Case-insensitive match[39m                                                                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - Simple substring check is fine; does not need full markdown parsing[39m                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Acceptance criteria[39m                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `hasInvestigationContent` helper detects all listed heading variants (case-insensitive)[39m                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] A bug labeled `needs-investigation` with a `## Investigation Report` in its body dispatches to `fix` phase, not `investigate`[39m                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] A notice is printed when this downgrade happens[39m                                                                                                      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] A bug labeled `needs-investigation` without prior investigation content still dispatches to `investigate` phase[39m                                      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] A bug without the label but with investigation content dispatches to `fix` phase (no change, default behavior)[39m                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] Unit test covers all 4 combinations (label × investigation content)[39m                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `go build ./...` and `go vet ./...` pass[39m                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Out of scope[39m                                                                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Changing the investigate skill behavior[39m                                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Adding new heading formats beyond the 4 listed (can be extended later via gotchas)[39m                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Design Context (from cb-7aa91d)[39m                                                                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Dispatch reliability: Stop hook, fix-phase for bugs, auto pipeline runs**[39m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Problem[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mDispatched agents are failing to complete their work reliably. Of 4 recent dispatches (pf-70df40, pf-326239, pf-09df7a, pf-21779f), none ran `cobuild [39m     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mcomplete`, three had CLAUDE.md corruption (already fixed), and the remaining three each stalled for a different reason.[39m                                    [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m… +475 lines …[39m                                                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231miptions | Update to reflect new default |[39m                                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m| `cobuild explain` output | Pipeline explanation | Already reads from config/skills, but verify it renders the new workflows correctly and mentions the [39m  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mescalation |[39m                                                                                                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m### Discoverability checks for the orchestrator agent (M)[39m                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mThe orchestrator agent (the one calling `cobuild dispatch`) is the most likely caller to need this. Before creating a bug work item, M should:[39m             [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. Read the bug symptoms from the user[39m                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Mentally run through the 7 escalation criteria[39m                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m3. If any apply, add `--label needs-investigation` when creating the work item[39m                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m4. If creating via skill, the skill should prompt M to make this decision explicitly[39m                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mThis belongs in the CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md that the orchestrator reads, in the "creating work items" section. It should be a small decision tree, not [39m      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mburied prose.[39m                                                                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m### Fail-loud signal[39m                                                                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mIf dispatch ever routes a bug to the `fix` phase and the fix agent realises mid-session that the cause is genuinely unknown or the blast radius is [39m        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231munclear, it should:[39m                                                                                                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. Stop implementing[39m                                                                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Append findings so far to the bug[39m                                                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m3. Add the `needs-investigation` label[39m                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m4. Exit and let the orchestrator re-dispatch through the investigation flow[39m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mThis self-escalation path prevents agents from flailing on bugs they can't fix safely.[39m                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
