[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Add escalation criteria to `skills/fix/fix-bug.md` with inline decision checklist[39m                                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Add bug-creation guidance to CLAUDE.md / generated AGENTS.md: "when creating a bug, apply these criteria to decide labeling"[39m                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Add self-escalation protocol to `skills/fix/fix-bug.md`[39m                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Verify `cobuild explain` renders the new workflows cleanly[39m                                                                                               [49m
